{"tid":1858543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆卦] 武漢肺炎病毒導致多人街頭暴斃的原因","createTime":"2020-02-02T18:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:06:33.000Z","uid":76705,"like":393,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdb8d97d4a8e118de9f191ab884f5d1168f65bc","tid":1858543,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:23:07.000Z","msg":"網絡上大量的信息都只說武漢冠狀病毒會造成肺部感染，這是非常片面的。實際上這種冠<br />\n狀病毒因為蛋白質與人體具有非常高的親和性，很容易騙過人體防禦機制。<br />\n<br />\n人體的心臟細胞經過高度進化，通常情況下不會被病毒入侵，但是這種病毒卻可以輕易感<br />\n染到心肌。因為心肌缺乏痛感反應，患者會毫無徵兆突然倒地死亡。<br />\n<br />\n因為武漢冠狀病毒導致的心肌炎和神經感染症狀並不明顯，所以很難引起患者注意，患者<br />\n基本上沒有痛感，也沒有咳嗽發燒等症狀。只會有輕微胸悶氣短。但是這種感染危險程度<br />\n和致死率遠超過肺部感染。導致大量患者毫無徵兆的倒地死亡。共產黨官方目前仍然在極<br />\n力掩蓋真相，導致大量患者缺乏防護意識突然倒地死亡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1580667603.A.9BA.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1580667603.A.9BA.html&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=0f6e4766\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1580667603.A.9BA.html</a>"},{"pid":"7aecd3a06720c9e5679a2ff48c64f4a405335ecf","tid":1858543,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8b0f9e82610629a8b89c978423261074f0047e6d","tid":1858543,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"606871a91cbceaac91254c5db65d8be42cc1ed0f","tid":1858543,"uid":76705,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"Need FC<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1n8Axg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1n8Axg.jpg&h=c98a20ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56935e31fc156ee8f512a335165ae99a6af1f755","tid":1858543,"uid":2419,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:29:24.000Z","msg":"痴撚線生化武器"},{"pid":"c094496024d261353a7ce687d7997add82bf62c7","tid":1858543,"uid":76705,"