b841421867e534cd85edb8070fb8526","tid":1858543,"uid":136987,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"Need fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"心肌炎的確會毫無先兆之下倒地<br />\n但武漢肺炎會唔會導致心肌炎就好難講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"會有d徵狀既 但好難發現"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://web.csh.org.tw/web/222010/?p=2179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.csh.org.tw%2Fweb%2F222010%2F%3Fp%3D2179&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=47cbc2bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.csh.org.tw/web/222010/?p=2179</a><br />\n臨床表現<br />\n<br />\n急性心肌炎的臨床表現千變萬化而無明顯特異性，一開始看似輕微的感冒或腸胃炎，最終可能演變成致命性休克的心肌炎，病程進展迅速突然，措手不及。病情輕者無明顯症狀，而病情重者卻可在數小時或數日內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n心肌炎的症狀容易被病毒感染引起的全身性症狀「轉移焦點」而忽略。急性心肌炎在發病前常是一般非特異性的上呼吸道感染或腸胃炎的症狀，如發燒、咳嗽、喉嚨痛、嘔吐、腹瀉、肌肉酸痛、疲倦無力、蒼白及心悸、胸悶痛、異常心音或心雜音、心搏過速或過緩、心律不整等，造成診斷上的困難。"},{"pid":"41d1ccdde492c5a062ec363caf9e3f739465a4b7","tid":1858543,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:36:11.000Z","msg":"alert"},{"pid":"a879f9bfe365a39cf38ee326d13b305ef08725c2","tid":1858543,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:38:02.000Z","msg":"生化災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73868fbbb03324d2c2dbf7f7920bb1d4e3794a4","tid":1858543,"uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4J38VL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4J38VL.jpg&h=47f84694&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3429589066b23c11045c3a6ca01b1c47efc19e17","tid":1858543,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"仲勁過心臟病發，起碼有咩黃金20分鐘<br />\n呢隻無啦啦就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{